1. Run the webserver in test mode
    script/server -e test -p 4000
2. Run the Selenium Server
    script/selenium
3. Run your story
    ruby stories/runner/anonynous_visit.rb


TROUBLESHOOTING
* If cannot find FIREFOX, set env vars to your Firefox lib dir (for step 2 and 3)
    export SELENIUM_BROWSER="*firefox /usr/lib/firefox/firefox-2-bin"
    export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="/usr/lib/firefox $LD_LIBRARY_PATH"
